    MAZ  Morocco, Africa.
    EGZ  Egypt, Africa.
    GHZ  Ghana, Africa.
    PEZ  Peru, South America.
    MYZ  Malaysia, Asia.
    THZ  Thailand, Asia.
    IDZ  Indonesia, Asia.
    KRZ  South Korea, Asia.
    HKZ  Hong Kong, Asia.
    INZ  India, Asia.
    AUZ  Australia.
    NZZ  New Zealand.
    BRZ  Brazil, South America.
    ARZ  Argentina, South America.
    VEZ  Venezuela, South America.
</CN>
<XX>
